examples.en: Eastern religions used to be the fashion in the 60s.
We were never taught anything about other religions.
There are many religions, such as Buddhism, Christianity, Hinduism, Islam, and Judaism.
Notwithstanding differences, there are clear similarities in all of the world's religions.
Some religions believe that the same spirit is reincarnated many times in different bodies.
Some religions teach that wicked people will suffer eternal punishment in hell after they die.
As the nexus for three great religions, Jerusalem has had a troubled as well as illustrious history.
